@startwbs
* AgenticNativePlatform - Current Runtime Architecture
** 1. North-south entry flow
*** External client
**** sends HTTP /v1 and /mcp
*** public-gateway
**** package: kgateway-system
**** Envoy data plane
**** kgateway is the north-south entry point
**** routed traffic goes to agentgateway-proxy
*** agentgateway-proxy
**** package: agentgateway-system
**** Gateway + Service :8080
**** agentgateway is the protocol-aware AI gateway
**** /v1 route -> litellm-upstream backend
**** /mcp route -> kagent-tools-mcp-backend
**** backend policy requestTimeout=300s applies to litellm-upstream

** 2. Cluster control-plane components
*** kgateway-system
**** kgateway controller
**** public-gateway
*** agentgateway-system
**** agentgateway controller
**** agentgateway-proxy
**** AgentgatewayBackend: litellm-upstream
**** AgentgatewayBackend: kagent-tools-mcp-backend
**** AgentgatewayPolicy: requestTimeout=300s
*** kagent
**** kagent-controller, Deployment + Service :8083
**** kagent-ui, Deployment + Service :8080
**** kagent-tools, Deployment + Service :8084
**** Agent: k8s-a2a-agent
**** RemoteMCPServer: kagent-tool-server
*** kmcp-system
**** kmcp-controller-manager
*** ai-models
**** tei-embeddings, Deployment + Service
**** KServe controller + webhook
**** optional runtime overlay
***** Ollama
***** vLLM
*** context
**** Qdrant
**** PostgreSQL
**** Redis
*** observability
**** Prometheus operator + Prometheus
**** Grafana
**** Loki
*** istio-system
**** istiod
**** istio-cni
**** ztunnel
*** cert-manager
**** cert-manager
**** cert-manager-webhook
**** cert-manager-cainjector
*** metallb-system
**** only for host-based profiles
**** metallb controller + speaker
*** optional sample path
**** MCPServer echo-mcp

** 3. Runtime request and data paths
*** Kagent UI / API flow
**** kagent-ui -> kagent-controller
**** k8s-a2a-agent -> kagent-controller
**** kagent-controller -> agentgateway-proxy via /v1
*** MCP flow
**** RemoteMCPServer kagent-tool-server -> agentgateway-proxy via /mcp/kagent-tools
**** agentgateway-proxy -> kagent-tools-mcp-backend -> kagent-tools
*** LLM flow
**** agentgateway-proxy -> litellm-upstream -> litellm
**** litellm -> remote LLM providers
***** Gemini
***** OpenAI
***** Anthropic
***** Bedrock
***** Vertex
***** others
**** litellm -> optional external LM Studio when LMSTUDIO_ENABLED=true
**** litellm -> runtime overlay when RUNTIME=ollama or vllm
**** KServe is installed in the serving stack but is not in the default /v1 hot path
*** Context and state flow
**** kagent-controller -> tei-embeddings for embeddings
**** kagent-controller -> Qdrant for vector context
**** kagent-controller -> PostgreSQL for structured state
**** kagent-controller -> Redis for cache / queue
*** Sample path
**** kmcp-controller-manager -> MCPServer echo-mcp

** 4. Profile presence notes
*** Context services are present in
**** platform-profile-full
**** platform-profile-fast-context
*** Observability is present in
**** platform-profile-full
